Lemminkaeinen Adds Profitability, Seeks 50 Million-Euro Savings

-- B y   K a t i   P o h j a n p a l o
-- 
2011-10-10T06:05:05Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-10/lemminkaeinen-adds-profitability-seeks-50-million-euro-savings.html
Lemminkaeinen Oyj said it seeks 50
million euros of savings a year from an efficiency-improvement
program that “most likely” won’t avoid impact on personnel.  The company kept its full-year guidance unchanged and
confirmed previous financial targets even as it seeks to boost
profitability, Lemminkaeinen said in a statement today.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Kati Pohjanpalo at 
 kpohjanpalo@bloomberg.net  